Someone I looked up to and a personal hero ..Rosalind Cash, from an interview nearly 40 years ago, speaking on the potent impact of her culture at home with the international community, and the reaction to it when she took acting jobs overseas. The response, she relays, affirmed her sense of deserving equal prominence and recognition in the industry, and all of its platforms 💯 #RosalindCash #actingbeast #warrior 👊🏾
